Interface SynthConstants

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Note, NoteNode, Sequence, SynthListener, SynthSys, SynthSysNode

    public interface SynthConstants
    Constant interface used to divide all the major constants used for the SynthListener class as well as other classes interacting with it.
    Author:
    John Falco
    Version:
    1.1
